snippet.title: 101 Ways To Die Launch Trailer PEGI
snippet.description: Check out gruesome new puzzle platformer 101 Ways To Die - available now for PC, PlayStation 4 and XBox One.  For more information on the game, please see http://101waystodiegame.com/
